This simple socket programming using while and if else statement perform below action:-

if client request " hello, who are you?"
server will reply " hi, my name is ( server ip)"

if client request "  what is your domain?
server will reply " my domain is fskm.edu.my"

for others request 
server will reply " i dont know"

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Client side
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
There are predefine respond message can be send to server.
These selection are using integer.
For example if client want to send Hello who are you, key in 1 as the selection
print("++++++++++++ MENU UTAMA ++++++++++++")
    print("+ 1. Hello who are you             +")
    print("+ 2. What is your domain?          +")
    print("+ 3. Who is the web Admin          +")
    print("+ 4. exit                          +")
    print("++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++")

Message print by the server based on selection keyin by the client.

++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++=
Server side
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
In order to respond to client enquiry, server must keyin the interfger based on 
predefine respond givem.
For example, if server reciever Hello who are you, key in integer 1 as the selection
print("++++++++++++ Message from Client+++++++++++++++++++++")
print("Type 1 If client send Hello who are you             +")
print("Type 2 if client send What is your domain?          +")
print("Type 3 if None of the above                         +")
print("Type 4 to exit                                      +")
